  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Lost in Anomaly, you wake up on the 9th floor of an unknown building. Your goal is to reach the first floor and escape from here. To get out of here, you must detect and mark anomalies. If you have marked all the anomalies, the elevator will take you to the lower floor. You should check every place well and mark accordingly because if you miss an anomaly, the elevator will take you back to the 9th floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312020/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.poster.avif?t=1770324875\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312020/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.webm?t=1770324875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312020/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.mp4?t=1770324875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25-75 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and mark different anomalies on each floor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some anomalies can only be seen with a UV flashlight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a gaming experience that tests your observation skills.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Lost in Anomaly, you wake up on the 9th floor of an unknown building. Your goal is to reach the first floor and escape from here. To get out of here, you must detect and mark anomalies. If you have marked all the anomalies, the elevator will take you to the lower floor. You should check every place well and mark accordingly because if you miss an anomaly, the elevator will take you back to the 9th floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312020/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.poster.avif?t=1770324875\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312020/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.webm?t=1770324875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312020/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.mp4?t=1770324875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25-75 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and mark different anomalies on each floor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some anomalies can only be seen with a UV flashlight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a gaming experience that tests your observation skills.</p></li></ul>",
